 you do nonconsciously.

40:55.680 --> 40:57.240
 And there's so much evidence

40:57.240 --> 41:00.840
 that even the simple things you do,

41:00.840 --> 41:03.280
 you can make decisions,

41:03.280 --> 41:05.680
 you can make committed decisions about them,

41:05.680 --> 41:07.320
 the neurobiologist can say,

41:07.320 --> 41:12.240
