 And look, physics is always going to look

58:39.520 --> 58:42.640
 for ways in which you can describe the system

58:42.640 --> 58:47.520
 in a way which rises above the details.

58:47.520 --> 58:52.520
 And to the hard dyed, the wool biologist,

